title: BBC.Make.Me.Welsh.576p.HDTV.x264-MVGroup
description:
An exclusive insight into how one county in Wales is ensuring that all its children speak Welsh. For a whole year, cameras followed eight children from all over the world trying to make Gwynedd their new home. They're given 12 weeks to learn a new language before being sent to school, where everything is taught in Welsh.
